snippet.title: EA Sports Active 2 - Real Fitness Trailer | HD
snippet.description:
EA Sports Active 2 will have support for the Xbox 360 Kinect motion controller formerly known as Project Natal.

PRE-ORDER TODAY: EA Sports Active 2 - http://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B0042X8RB0?ie=UTF8&tag=xboxviewtv-21&linkCode=as2&camp=1638&creative=6742&creativeASIN=B0042X8RB0
